# CODEOWNERS — OraclousAI/oraclous-frontend
#
# Maps code ownership so GitHub requests reviews from the right team.
# Each rule is last-match-wins; more specific patterns are listed after
# less specific ones so they override correctly.
#
# Teams:
#   @OraclousAI/devops    — infra, CI/CD, deployment manifests, config
#   @OraclousAI/frontend  — application code, design system, packages

# ─── Default: every file requires both teams ─────────────────────────────────
*                                @OraclousAI/devops @OraclousAI/frontend

# ─── Application code ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
/apps/                           @OraclousAI/frontend
/packages/                       @OraclousAI/frontend

# ─── Infrastructure / CI / config ────────────────────────────────────────────
/.github/                        @OraclousAI/devops
/CODEOWNERS                      @OraclousAI/devops
/.env.example                    @OraclousAI/devops
